room_title: Escape room "The Parlor" by Escape 20/20 in Grand Rapids
review: Worst 25$ I’ve spend. I have tried an escape room another place before and this was no where near in quality, originality or fun. Not only did we have to share a room with a group of strangers, we didn’t get a background story as we were supposed to stated on the website, and we simply got bored! This is not how an escape room should be! Wouldn’t recommend this to anyone.
